TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT A.CPG_DESC AS CALC_CPG_DESC , A.CPG_CODE AS CPG_CODE FROM FCST_CPG_CONTROL A, XRF_ACC B WHERE A.POS_BY_STORE_IND = 'Y' AND A.CPG_CODE = B.GRP_CDE AND B.TS_DIV_CDE = 'SP' AND A.CPG_CODE NOT IN('BB', 'CR')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TOP 1 DIM_WEEK.FISCAL_YR, DIM_WEEK.FISCAL_MTH_NUM, DIM_WEEK.FISCAL_WK_OF_YR, MIN(DIM_WEEK.AS_OF_DATE_INT) AS CALC_STARTDATE FROM DBO.DIM_WEEK WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE AS_OF_DATE_INT >= CAST(FORMAT(GETDATE()-7,'yyyyMMdd') AS INT) GROUP BY FISCAL_YR,FISCAL_MTH_NUM, FISCAL_WK_OF_YR
